INSERT INTO `teacher` VALUES ('0001','Ahmed Abou-aeid','（性别信息未找到）','1943','','0451-86412041-899','ahmed.abou-zeid@t-online.de','Ahmed Abou-Zeid教授，1943年生，1974年德国布伦瑞克工业大学博士学位。德国联邦物理研究院5.4部前部长，中国国家外专局高端外国专家，哈尔滨工业大学兼职博导，在CIRP Annals、Optics Letters、Metrologia、Measurement Science and Technology等学术期刊发表论文117篇，领导(参与)欧盟和德联邦政府项目14项、企业合作项目6项，获德国发明专利授权1项（已成功转产），职务发明5项，并组织国际比对1次、欧盟计量基标准对口援建项目3次。','1. 2005年2月德国总统豪斯特科勒签授联邦政府;高级顾问和教授;头衔（Appointed as ;Director and Professor; by the President of Germany Horst K&ouml;hler）2. 欧盟和德联邦项目协调员；3. 第五届仪器科学与技术国际学术会议5th ISIST大会合作主席；4. 第六届精密工程测量与仪器国际学术会议6thISPEMI大会合作主席；5. 第九国际测量技术与智能仪器学术会议9th','--','--','123456'),('0002','Alam','（性别信息未找到）','（生日信息未找到）','机电工程学院','0755-2662347','alamm28@yahoo.com','  Alam Md. Mahbub is a professor atthe Shenzhen Graduate School of Harbin Institute of Technology (China) since 2012. He worked as a senior lecturer at the University of Pretoria (South Africa), research and postdoctoral fellows at the Hong Kong Polytechnic University,and lecturer at the Rajshahi University of Engineering and Technology (Bangladesh).He received MEngand PhD degrees from Kitami Institute of Technology, Japan, in 2001 and 2004, all in Mechanical Engineering. More than 180technical articlesare authored and co-authored, including 66 journal papers, most of which have been published in the top-notched journals, including Journal of Fluid Mechanics, Journal of Fluids &amp; Structures, Physics of Fluids, Physical ReviewE, Journal of Sustainable and Energy Reviews. Seven of the journal papers got positions in the lists of ‘TOP 25 hottest articles’ and one paper has got a position in TOP 1% highly cited articlesin 2016 by THOMPSON REUTERS as of Science Indicator. He is the author of two books and 15 chapters in books. He has edited a special issue in ‘Wind and Structures, an International Journal’ and a conference proceeding published in Research publishing, Singapore. He has delivered 10 Keynote speeches atinternational conferences. His research has mostly involved fluid dynamics around single and multiple cylinders, flow-induced vibrations, fluid-structure interactions, airfoil aerodynamics, renewable energy, and flow controls. He has secured a total of RMB8 million research funding from national and international levels.  ProfAlam has received a number of awards: Japan Government Scholarship (monbusho) for Masters and PhD studies; JSPS (Japan Society for Promotion of Science) Postdoctoral fellowship; South Africa National Research Foundation (NRF) rating ‘Promising Young Researcher, Y1’;China 1000-young-talent scholar (青年千人计划);Shenzhen High-LevelOverseas Talent; Shenzhen High-Level Professional; 2015 Shenzhen Outstanding Teacher; and 2016 HIT Creative Talent Teacher. He has also received 05 best paper awards from different conferences.He is an editorial board member of ‘Wind and Structures, an International Journal’ and Chief Topic Editor of Frontiers: Bluff-Body Aerodynamics and Fluid-Structure Interactions. He has been acting as a reviewer for the top-level journals, e.g., Journal of Fluid Mechanics, Journal of Fluids and Structures, Experiments in Fluids, Physics of Fluids, Ocean Engineering, International Journal of Heat and Fluid Flow, Journal of Sound and Vibrations, Journal of Wind Engineering and Industrial Aerodynamics.','未找到个人荣誉信息','--','--','123456'),('0003','艾青','男','（生日信息未找到）','能源科学与工程学院','0451-86403764','hitaiqing@hit.edu.cn','艾青，男，汉族，博士，副教授，博士生导师；哈尔滨工业大学能源科学与工程学院航空航天热物理研究所教师。 ','未找到个人荣誉信息','--','--','123456'),('0004','安昊','（性别信息未找到）','（生日信息未找到）','航天学院','15804661244','hao.rc.an@gmail.com','安昊，就职于空间控制与惯性技术研究中心，博士后。研究方向：自适应控制、高超声速飞行器控制、无人机控制。兴趣爱好：航空模型设计、制作、飞行。','未找到个人荣誉信息','--','--','123456'),('0005','安亮','男','1985','能源科学与工程学院','','anliang@hit.edu.cn','安亮，男，汉族，1985年生，黑龙江齐齐哈尔人；博士，哈尔滨工业大学，能源科学与工程学院，教授，博士生导师。目前主要从事新能源转化与储存技术的基础与应用研究。','未找到个人荣誉信息','--','--','123456'),('0006','安茂忠','男','1985','化工与化学学院','86413721','mzan@hit.edu.cn','未找到个人简介信息','未找到个人荣誉信息','--','--','123456'),('0007','安群涛','男','（生日信息未找